"""
moltiplication element to element for 
python 

in the exemple:  actualisation of future cash flow 
please NOTE : I have created two variables (a and b) that are to be considered as temporary 
I am looking for a more efficient way to multiply the lists value element by element
"""
actualization_factor = [1 , 0.98, 0.97 ]
Future_cash_flows = [ 100 , 102 , 105 ]
listres = [] 
for X in range(3) :
    a = actualization_factor[X]
    b = float(Future_cash_flows[X]) 
    res = a * b
    listres.append( res) 

print (listres)
